    "name": "Unity-chan the SharpShooter!",
    "steam_appid": 3027580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027580/extras/4b7986b1d17b19ac5980ae4fcd836f15.avif?t=1765818043\" width=640 height=360 /></span><strong>&quot;Unity-chan the SharpShooter!&quot;</strong> is an old-school shooter inspired by NES Zapper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic controls are mouse-only, and one play takes about 10 minutes, making it easy to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This work consists of the following three games:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unitied Flying Object! - Clay Shooting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027580/extras/cb834c6d0fa7c6cd91af46dd14067257.avif?t=1765818043\" width=480 height=270 /></span><strong>Unity's Alley! - Rail Shooter</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027580/extras/41462786c3228bb133b4eb851de99f75.avif?t=1765818043\" width=480 height=270 /></span><strong>One Shot, One Break! - Sniping</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027580/extras/801f8dffd5e8aeafd22f7547c3593d10.avif?t=1765818043\" width=480 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game has three modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade</strong> - Stage-clear and score attack type game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free</strong> - No game over, and allows detailed settings for game speed, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Competition</strong> - based on actual shooting competitions.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, Extra games will be opened if you get a high score in the Arcade mode, and finally, 19 games will be available to play! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For a little free time</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For a break from AAA titles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For a change of pace in your workWould you like a shooter that you can casually play with?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STREAMING GUIDELINE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As long as it is not against the law or public order and morals, any individual or corporation can post and distribute videos without permission.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although it is not required, we would appreciate it if you could include a link to the Steam page in the summary section or elsewhere.</p>",
